        "id": 1153089
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-05-27T06:56:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks for writing the code. It looks a lot easier-to-read than what I suggested in my comment. I didn\u0027t know that maps default to empty value for items that do not exist and did not know about strings.Join function. I think it\u0027s fine to keep this logic inlined, but please let me know if you still want a separate function and I\u0027ll update the CL again.",
      "parentUuid": "45b083c2_d0a717f3",
      "revId": "f4f82c4640593ef4c05b174459f3e46a60fb7a58",
